title: Miele C3 CALIMA Canister Vacuum
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Miele C3 Calima canister vacuum.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/88834/Miele-Complete-C3-Calima-Yellow-Canister-Vacuum-41GFE036USA.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=C3CALIMA%20_2017077 

Features:
Silence motor with 6 speed settings controlled via +/- footswitch controls
36' operating radius
HEPA AirClean filter
STB 205-3 Turbo Brush
SBB 300-3 Parquet Twister
Recommended for low pile carpeting, rugs, & hard floors
